SELECT [l].[Id], [l].[AutorId], [l].[CreationTime], [l].[GeneroId], [l].[IsDeleted], [l].[Isbn], [l].[QrCode], [l].[Quantidade], [l].[Titulo]
FROM [Livros] AS [l]
INNER JOIN [Autores] AS [a] ON [l].[AutorId] = [a].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Generos] AS [g] ON [l].[GeneroId] = [g].[Id]

SELECT [l].[Id], [l].[AutorId], [l].[CreationTime], [l].[GeneroId], [l].[IsDeleted], [l].[Isbn], [l].[QrCode], [l].[Quantidade], [l].[Titulo]
FROM [Livros] AS [l]
INNER JOIN [Autores] AS [a] ON [l].[AutorId] = [a].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Generos] AS [g] ON [l].[GeneroId] = [g].[Id]

INFO  2024-01-28 15:14:56,371 [60   ] oft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command - Executed DbCommand (9ms) [Parameters=[@__input_Keyword_0='?' (Size = 4000)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [l].[Id], [l].[AutorId], [l].[CreationTime], [l].[GeneroId], [l].[IsDeleted], [l].[Isbn], [l].[QrCode], [l].[Quantidade], [l].[Titulo]
FROM [Livros] AS [l]
INNER JOIN [Autores] AS [a] ON [l].[AutorId] = [a].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Generos] AS [g] ON [l].[GeneroId] = [g].[Id]
WHERE ([l].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ((((@__input_Keyword_0 LIKE N'') OR (CHARINDEX(@__input_Keyword_0, [l].[Titulo]) > 0)) OR ((@__input_Keyword_0 LIKE N'') OR (CHARINDEX(@__input_Keyword_0, [a].[Nome]) > 0))) OR ((@__input_Keyword_0 LIKE N'') OR (CHARINDEX(@__input_Keyword_0, [g].[Descricao]) > 0)))

FROM [Livros] AS [l]

SELECT [l].[Id], [l].[AutorId], [l].[CreationTime], [l].[GeneroId], [l].[IsDeleted], [l].[Isbn], [l].[QrCode], [l].[Quantidade], [l].[Titulo]
FROM [Livros] AS [l]
INNER JOIN [Autores] AS [a] ON [l].[AutorId] = [a].[Id]

FROM [Livros] AS [l]

SELECT [l].[Id], [l].[AutorId], [l].[CreationTime], [l].[GeneroId], [l].[IsDeleted], [l].[Isbn], [l].[QrCode], [l].[Quantidade], [l].[Titulo]
FROM [Livros] AS [l]
INNER JOIN [Autores] AS [a] ON [l].[AutorId] = [a].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Generos] AS [g] ON [l].[GeneroId] = [g].[Id]

SELECT [l].[Id], [l].[AutorId], [l].[CreationTime], [l].[GeneroId], [l].[IsDeleted], [l].[Isbn], [l].[QrCode], [l].[Quantidade], [l].[Titulo]
FROM [Livros] AS [l]
INNER JOIN [Autores] AS [a] ON [l].[AutorId] = [a].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Generos] AS [g] ON [l].[GeneroId] = [g].[Id]
WHERE ([l].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ((((@__input_Keyword_0 LIKE N'') OR (CHARINDEX(@__input_Keyword_0, [l].[Titulo]) > 0)) OR ((@__input_Keyword_0 LIKE N'') OR (CHARINDEX(@__input_Keyword_0, [a].[Nome]) > 0))) OR ((@__input_Keyword_0 LIKE N'') OR (CHARINDEX(@__input_Keyword_0, [g].[Descricao]) > 0)))

SELECT [l].[Id], [l].[AutorId], [l].[CreationTime], [l].[GeneroId], [l].[IsDeleted], [l].[Isbn], [l].[QrCode], [l].[Quantidade], [l].[Titulo]
FROM [Livros] AS [l]
INNER JOIN [Autores] AS [a] ON [l].[AutorId] = [a].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Generos] AS [g] ON [l].[GeneroId] = [g].[Id]
WHERE ([l].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ((((@__input_Keyword_0 LIKE N'') OR (CHARINDEX(@__input_Keyword_0, [l].[Titulo]) > 0)) OR ((@__input_Keyword_0 LIKE N'') OR (CHARINDEX(@__input_Keyword_0, [a].[Nome]) > 0))) OR ((@__input_Keyword_0 LIKE N'') OR (CHARINDEX(@__input_Keyword_0, [g].[Descricao]) > 0)))

FROM [Livros] AS [l]
INNER JOIN [Autores] AS [a] ON [l].[AutorId] = [a].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Generos] AS [g] ON [l].[GeneroId] = [g].[Id]
WHERE ([l].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ((((@__input_Keyword_0 LIKE N'') OR (CHARINDEX(@__input_Keyword_0, [l].[Titulo]) > 0)) OR ((@__input_Keyword_0 LIKE N'') OR (CHARINDEX(@__input_Keyword_0, [a].[Nome]) > 0))) OR ((@__input_Keyword_0 LIKE N'') OR (CHARINDEX(@__input_Keyword_0, [g].[Descricao]) > 0)))

SELECT [l].[Id], [l].[AutorId], [l].[CreationTime], [l].[GeneroId], [l].[IsDeleted], [l].[Isbn], [l].[QrCode], [l].[Quantidade], [l].[Titulo]
FROM [Livros] AS [l]
INNER JOIN [Autores] AS [a] ON [l].[AutorId] = [a].[Id]

FROM [Livros] AS [l]

ORDER BY [a].[Priority] DESC, [a].[TryCount], [a].[NextTryTime]
